                <h3>Objetivos</h3>

                <p>Fornecer fundamentos te√≥ricos sobre vetores, retas no espa√ßo e plano (com suas rela√ß√µes), c√¥nicas e qu√°dricas, t√≥picos essenciais no estudo de todas Engenharias</p>
                <p><i>The discipline aims at providing theoretical foundation regarding vectors, lines and planes (with their relations), conic sections and quadric surfaces, which are essential matters in the study of Engineering.</i></p>

                <h3>Docente(s) Respons√°vel(eis)</h3>

                <ul>
                    
