                </ul>

                <h3>Programa resumido</h3>

                <p>Sequencias e s√©ries, equa√ß√µes diferenciais ordin√°rias de 1¬™ e 2¬™ ordem com aplica√ß√µes, solu√ß√£o de equa√ß√µes diferenciais por series de potencia, S√©ries de Fourier e Problemas de valores de contorno.</p>
                <p><i>Sequences and series, first and second order ordinary differential equations, Solution of equations differential equations by power series, Fourier series and boundary value problems.</i></p>

                <h3>Programa</h3>

                <p>Sequ√™ncias e s√©ries: Crit√©rios de converg√™ncia, converg√™ncia condicional e absoluta, s√©ries de pot√™ncia, raio de converg√™ncia, deriva√ß√£o e integra√ß√£o termo a termo. Equa√ß√µes diferenciais ordin√°rias de 1¬™ e 2¬™ ordem: Equa√ß√µes exatas e n√£o exatas, redu√ß√£o de ordem, Equa√ß√£o de Bernulli, m√©todo de varia√ß√£o de par√¢metros e coeficientes a determinar, solu√ß√£o por s√©ries de potencia de equa√ß√µes diferenciais, aplica√ß√µes das equa√ß√µes diferenciais de 1¬™ e 2¬™ ordem.‚Ä¢S√©ries de Fourier: Teorema de converg√™ncia das s√©ries de Fourier, Desigualdade de Bessel e Identidade de Parseval, equa√ß√µes em derivadas parciais e problemas de valores de contorno.</p>
                <p><i>‚Ä¢Sequences and series: Convergence criteria, absolute and conditional convergence, power series, radius convergence, Derivatives and integration term to term.‚Ä¢First and second order ordinary differential equations : Exact and non-exact differential equations, order reduction, Bernulli equation, the method of undetermined coefficients an variations of parameters, solution of differential equations by power series, applications of first and second order differential equations.‚Ä¢Fourier series: Fourier series convergence theorem, Bessel‚Äôs Inequality and Parseval‚Äôs identity, Partial differential equations and boundary value problems.</i></p>

                <h3>Avalia√ß√£o</h3>
