                <p><i>1. Characterization of production programming and control. 2. Demand management. 3. Aggregate Production Planning. 4. Master Production Schedulling. 5. Inventory planning and control. 6. Material Requirement Planning (meP). 7. Production Schedulling. 8. Detailed scheduling of production. 9. Just In Time (JIT). 10. Theory of Constraints (TOC). 11. Production control systems.</i></p>

